included.description:
Harvest is a food delivery service aggregator operating in Austin, TX. Their aim is to provide users with a single website to visit when placing orders for delivery. They combine the restaurant options of 11 delivery services to provide the greatest overall reach for delivery options in the Austin area.

My work for Harvest focused on research of both competitors and users. I performed a thorough analysis of six delivery services to compare their designs, labeling, and features to gather design requirements for the Harvest website. I then carried out a usability testing plan to determine what worked, what didn't, and what new features users wanted Harvest to develop.
